Description: AWS SDK for Python (Avalan PPA transitive)
 boto3 is the official AWS SDK for Python. It builds on botocore
 and s3transfer to expose high-level resource and service clients.
 This package is built for the Avalan PPA because aioboto3
 (Avalan's `vendors` extra) reaches it transitively through
 aiobotocore and Noble ships an older 1.34.46 line. Pinned at
 1.40.61, the top of the aiobotocore window.
